creator: Life Plus Bangladesh Limited
descriptionHtml:
LifePlus BD is an one-stop digital healthcare service . Through this app, we will continuously offer new and useful healthcare services which will ensure better healthcare for you & your loved ones.
This app is going to bring ease to your healthcare journey ! It will enable you to order pharmaceutical and healthcare products online and get them delivered to your doorstep. We are an online medical store, making your next medical purchase easy, simple, and affordable! Through our app, you can purchase medicines online & get it delivered to your doorstep within 4-6 hours inside Dhaka City.
LifePlus BD App helps you to make appointments with qualified doctors online quickly with ease. It also makes it easy for you to buy healthcare products , OTC products & medical equipments online. You can book diagnostic tests online, including blood tests, lab tests, full body checkup & other preventive health checkups from the convenience of your home. We offer our app users multiple health check-up package as per user requirements.
Features:
· Online booking of Doctors Appointment;
· Booking for diagnostic tests online inside Dhaka;
· Medical report home delivery service within 24 hours inside Dhaka City;
· Nursing home care service;
· 24X7 Ambulance calling service;
· One-tap hotline service;
· Call for Ambulance through the app;
· Order pharmaceutical and healthcare products online and get Home Delivery within 24 hours inside Dhaka City;
So, keep an eye out for regular updates to enjoy our upcoming services!
